クラス WarzoneListener

java.lang.Object
io.github.townyadvanced.flagwar.listeners.WarzoneListener
すべての実装されたインタフェース:
org.bukkit.event.Listener
public class WarzoneListener extends Object implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
WarZone Listener, ported from Towny.

    コンストラクタ
    コンストラクタ
    説明
    WarzoneListener()
    Sets the Towny instance at construction.

  • メソッドの概要

    修飾子とタイプ
    メソッド
    説明
    void
    onBuild(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.actions.TownyBuildEvent townyBuildEvent)
    When the TownyBuildEvent is fired, check if PlayerCache.TownBlockStatus.ENEMY is accurate and that the item being used is in the allowed items list in the WarZone section of the FlagWar Configuration.
    void
    onBurn(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.actions.TownyBurnEvent townyBurnEvent)
    When Towny reports a burn event, check if this is a PlayerCache.TownBlockStatus which corresponds to a Cell which is under attack, and the FlagWar Config is configured to allow fires in WarZones.
    void
    onDestroy(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.actions.TownyDestroyEvent townyDestroyEvent)
    When the TownyDestroyEvent is fired, check if PlayerCache.TownBlockStatus.ENEMY is accurate and that the item being used is in the allowed items list in the WarZone section of the FlagWar Configuration.
    void
    onExplosionDamagingBlocks(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.actions.TownyExplodingBlocksEvent event)
    When Towny reports an explosion damaging some blocks, check if this is a PlayerCache.TownBlockStatus which corresponds to a Cell which is under attack, and the FlagWar Config is configured to allow those explosions in WarZones.
    void
    onExplosionDamagingEntity(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.damage.TownyExplosionDamagesEntityEvent townyExplosionDamagesEntityEvent)
    When Towny reports an explosion damaging an entity event, check if this is a PlayerCache.TownBlockStatus which corresponds to a Cell which is under attack, and the FlagWar Config is configured to allow those explosions in WarZones.
    void
    onItemUse(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.actions.TownyItemuseEvent townyItemuseEvent)
    When Towny reports an item has been used: check if PlayerCache.TownBlockStatus.ENEMY is accurate and that the item being used is in the allowed items list in the WarZone section of the FlagWar Configuration.
    void
    onSwitchUse(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.actions.TownySwitchEvent townySwitchEvent)
    When Towny reports a switch has been used: check if PlayerCache.TownBlockStatus.ENEMY is accurate and that the use of switches is enabled in the WarZone section of the FlagWar Configuration.
    void
    onTownBlockPVPTestEvent(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.event.damage.TownBlockPVPTestEvent townBlockPVPTestEvent)
    When Towny asks if PVP should be enabled in a TownBlock, if it is a Cell which is under attack, we will tell Towny that PVP should be enabled, overriding any Town or TownBlock setting.
